                    "content": "<style type=\"text/css\">\n    video {\n        padding-bottom: 70px;\n        width: 100%;\n        margin: 0 auto;\n        z-index: -2;\n    }\n\n    .snakify-alumni {\n        background-color: #eeeeee;\n        padding-top: 80px;\n        padding-bottom: 50px;\n    }\n\n    .snakify-alumni-card {\n        display: inline-block;\n        background-color: #efe;\n        width: 300px;\n        min-height: 400px;\n        vertical-align: top;\n        margin-bottom: 40px;\n        margin-top: 20px;\n    }\n\n    .snakify-alumni-card:not(:last-of-type) {\n        margin-right: 40px;\n    }\n\n    .snakify-alumni-card-name {\n        font-size: 24px;\n        padding-top: 50px;\n    }\n\n    .snakify-alumni-card-location {\n        font-size: 14px;\n        padding-top: 15px;\n    }\n\n    .snakify-alumni-card img {\n        width: 150px;\n        padding-top: 30px;\n    }\n\n    .snakify-alumni-card-reference {\n        font-size: 14px;\n        padding: 30px 20px 30px 20px;\n    }\n\n    .snakify-facts {\n        margin-left: -100px;\n        background-color: #eeffee;\n        padding-left: 200px;\n        margin-top: 60px;\n        /*padding-right: 40px;*/\n    }\n\n    .snakify-facts h6 {\n        font-size: 20px;\n        font-weight: 200;\n        margin-bottom: 20px;\n    }\n\n    .snakify-facts .column {\n        text-align: center;\n        padding-top: 60px;\n        padding-bottom: 40px;\n    }\n\n    .snakify-facts .column h5 {\n        font-size: 26px;\n        margin-bottom: 0;\n    }\n\n    button.snakify-button-start {\n        background-color: #ff4444;\n        width: 500px;\n        height: 80px;\n        color: white;\n        font-size: 34px;\n        border: 0;\n        margin: 70px auto 0 auto;\n        display: block;\n    }\n\n    button.snakify-button-start a {\n        color: white;\n    }\n\n    .school-logo {\n        height: 60px;\n        margin: 20px;\n    }\n</style>\n\n<p>Let's see how to add two numbers in Python. Run this example:",
