                    "content": "<div class=\"snakify-full-width\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n    <div class=\"snakify-alumni-card\">\n        <div class=\"snakify-alumni-card-name\">John Sloan</div>\n        <div class=\"snakify-alumni-card-location\">Dublin, Ireland</div>\n        <img src=\"/static/images/alumni/sloan.jpeg\">\n        <div class=\"snakify-alumni-card-reference\">\u201cI was a linguist looking to move into computational linguistics but had no background in CS. Snakify took me from absolute beginner to top of the class. I have now designed a website with online English classes and received funding for further research.\u201d</div>\n    </div>\n\n\n    <div class=\"snakify-alumni-card\">\n        <div class=\"snakify-alumni-card-name\">Evgeny Serebryakov</div>\n        <div class=\"snakify-alumni-card-location\">Saint-Petersburg, Russia</div>\n        <img src=\"/static/images/alumni/serebryakov.png\">\n        <div class=\"snakify-alumni-card-reference\">\u201cI was studying molecular biophysics at my university. In spring 2015 I completed this course and then in winter I found a first internship as a Python/Django web developer.\u201d</div>\n    </div>\n</div>",
